text: Milosav Sićović (; born 12 November 1999) is a Serbian football midfielder who plays for FK Radnički Niš. ==Club career== After he spent his youth career with Internacional Beograd, in summer 2018 he signed with Dinamo Vranje.Фудбал 29/18 at Football Association of Serbia, 18-7-2018 Sićović made his official debut for Dinamo Vranje in 1 fixture match of the 2018–19 Serbian SuperLiga season against Red Star. ==Career statistics== ===Club=== {| class="wikitable" style="text-align: center;font-size:90%" |+ Appearances and goals by club, season and competition |- !rowspan="2"|Club !rowspan="2"|Season !colspan="3"|League !colspan="2"|Cup !colspan="2"|Continental !colspan="2"|Other !colspan="2"|Total |- !Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals |- |valign="center"|Dinamo Vranje |2018–19 ||SuperLiga ||9||0||0||0||0||0||colspan="2"|—||9||0 |- !colspan="3"|Career total !9!!0!!0!!0!!1!!0!!colspan="2"|—!!9!!0 |} ==References== ==External links== * * Profile at srbijafudbal.com Category:People from Zemun Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Association football defenders Category:Serbian footballers Category:FK Dinamo Vranje players Category:FK Kabel players Category:FK Sinđelić Beograd players Category:Serbian SuperLiga players Category:Serbian First League players
